cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NE 

This paper is about lossy image compression using deep convolutional neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel tucker decomposition layer and an iterative quantization scheme, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), and neural networks (cs.NE).
